Kotlin version Compose version Calf version 2.2.21 1.9.2 0.9.0 2.1.21 1.8.0 0.8.0 2.1.10 1.7.3 0.7.1 2.1.0 1.7.3 0.7.0 2.0.21 1.7.0 0.6.1 2.0.10 1.6.11 0.5.5 1.9.22 1.6.0 0.4.1 1.9.21 1.5.11 0.3.1 1.9.20 1.5.10 0.2.0 1.9.0 1.5.0 0.1.1 <p>Add the following dependencies to your module <code>build.gradle.kts</code> file:</p> <pre><code>// For Adaptive UI components
api("com.mohamedrejeb.calf:calf-ui:0.9.0")

// For WebView
implementation("com.mohamedrejeb.calf:calf-webview:0.9.0")

// For FilePicker
implementation("com.mohamedrejeb.calf:calf-file-picker:0.9.0")

// For Permissions
implementation("com.mohamedrejeb.calf:calf-permissions:0.9.0")
</code></pre> <p>If you are using <code>calf-ui</code> artifact, make sure to export it to binaries:</p>

Material (Android, Desktop, Web) Cupertino (iOS) <pre><code>Box(
    modifier = Modifier
        .size(100.dp)
        .background(Color.Red, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
        .adaptiveClickable(
            // Optional parameters
            shape = RoundedCornerShape(8.dp),
            interactionSource = remember { MutableInteractionSource() },
            indication = rememberRipple(), // Used on Android only
            enabled = true,
        ) {
            // Handle click
            println("Clicked!")
        }
)
</code></pre>
